  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And these people were-- I mean, it was something like some satisfaction where, in a certain, little way, I was able to make them feel what I felt, in, in, in a certain way, which was never in the same-- in the same, massive way, you know.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we have transported-- put them on the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Them-- those people, even, even, the people-- the cleaning people because we didn't want to-- the Russian-- the Russian didn't want to leave anybody left, left out.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Everybody had to be transported to, to Russia in order to bring back-- to build back the factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And-- because they had the whole-- the equipment, and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Fortunately for those guys, afterwards, I found out that these factories were sent to Leningrad, some of them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they wound up somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the Russians were completely disorganized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And, and till today, I don't know whether these factories were ever brought to fruition.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But at least for me, it was a incredible, incredible experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I have to go on with this and, and, and explain to you my escape.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
